name: Aqua Energy
effect: Aqua Energy can be attached only to a Pokémon with Team Aqua in its name. Aqua Energy provides {W} and {D} Energy but provides 2 Energy at a time. (Doesn’t count as a basic Energy card when not in play and has no effect other than providing Energy.) At the end of your turn, discard Aqua Energy.
author: Takumi Akabane
